Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.73,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}バイバイ　あたしきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:05:01.25,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}絶対辿り着く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:06.16,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:22.34,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}行きずりの男たちに　蹴りをつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:28.02,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}満たされない　この街からの「Set me free」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:35.25,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}何一ついい思い出はないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:41.07,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}此処で見る星はちょっとキレイね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:47.66,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}まだこの身体が覚えてる欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.87,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}だけど　何か足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:57.05,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}叶うことない夢の一欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:04.85,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}バイバイ　戻らない　二度と戻れない　Let me be…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:12.81,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}どんな孤独も　昨日に投げ棄てて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.06,Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}Breakin' Down
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.73,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}拜拜  我一定可以
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.73,0:05:01.25,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}绝对能抵达终点
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.16,0:05:06.16,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}Don't bother!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.09,0:05:22.34,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}与那些萍水相逢的男人们  从此一刀两断
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.60,0:05:28.02,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}在这座永不满足的城市中  大喊「Set me free」
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.14,0:05:35.25,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}尽管在这里没有一点美好的回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.98,0:05:41.07,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}但此处的星星却格外美丽
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.07,0:05:47.66,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}这副身体还残留着欲望
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.87,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}可心中  仍觉得缺少了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.87,0:05:57.05,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}是那无法实现的梦想的残片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.38,0:06:04.85,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}拜拜  我不会回头  绝对不会再回头  Let me be…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.85,0:06:12.81,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}无论怎样的孤独  都抛向昨日
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.06,Song - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4\fax-0.2}Breakin' Down
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Movie End]
